name: Becca Dayton
coverLetter: Never trimmed, never tried. I want to learn like everyone else. I want to dive in and learn as much as I can. I want to grow with this booming business because I know I would be amazing at it. I am a person who works 5 to 5 every day and want a change of pace to fulfill the path I seek. This will help me get there. Give me a chance and I'll blow your mind.
